playbookOutput.executionSummary:
Provider: "I want to set up ACH/EFT payments for my pharmacy. Can you guide me through the process?"

Agent: "Absolutely. You'll need to complete the ACH/EFT Request Form. This requires your banking information, including the bank name, routing number, and account number. Did you receive the form, or do you need it sent to you?"

Provider: "I need the form sent to me, please."

Agent: "I can email that to you directly. Once you fill it out, you can email it back to provider.relations@changehealthcare.com or fax it to 615-340-6160. Ensure you include a voided check or a bank letter to validate the account information."

Provider: "And how long does it take to process?"

Agent: "Once we receive your completed form, the information will be effective approximately 2 weeks from the date of receipt. You'll receive an email confirmation once it's processed."
